content: They are going to be in the area tomorrow and I will be there at 8:00 and I can come in tomorrow at the latest so I can get a ride.

I always played this as a kid on the computer. When my kids play they click a lot thinking its like an app so that's something parents should watch and explain. My only complaint is the music is crazy loud so I have it turned off or the characters can't be heard. Other than that it brings back great memories.
Can't wait till my little one can play the games I grew up playing. That you so much for making these an app. I'm voting for Freddie Fish and Fatty Bear next!
The screen is off-center to the right on the Galaxy Tablet. Will make things difficult for kids.
I love this game! No problems with any of the features. It's just like being 5 again!
